native_form.query: SELECT CAST("PUBLIC"."ORDERS"."CREATED_AT" AS date) AS "CREATED_AT", SUM("PUBLIC"."ORDERS"."TOTAL") AS "sum" FROM "PUBLIC"."ORDERS" GROUP BY CAST("PUBLIC"."ORDERS"."CREATED_AT" AS date) ORDER BY CAST("PUBLIC"."ORDERS"."CREATED_AT" AS date) ASC
